Guacamole with Pomegranate Seeds

10 min
$6.5
220 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-FreeVegetarian

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

AppetizerHealthyQuick

Description

A creamy and refreshing guacamole topped with vibrant pomegranate seeds for a burst of flavor.

Ingredients

  • ripe avocados: 2
  • lime juice: 1
  • salt: 1/2 teaspoon
  • pomegranate seeds: 1/2 cup
  • chopped cilantro: 2 tablespoons
  • diced red onion: 1/4 cup
  • diced tomato: 1 medium
  • jalape単o (optional): 1 small
